node.text:
Happy Women’s Equality day! Today is an important day for me and I want to make sure young women are succeeding in their education. 

I’m putting up a $10,000 scholarship for any student between the ages of 13-23 in North America. Download the SportsHi app to check it out, it takes less than 5 minutes and you don’t have to be playing sports to apply!

Can’t wait to go through y’all’s applications!

#womensequality #womensequalityday #sportshi4women
